# Legacy reference code

This path is **read-only parity reference** — not the live deployment target.

## Runtime constraints

Google Apps Script: no ES modules (`import`/`export`), UI calls the server via `google.script.run`, GAS globals (`SpreadsheetApp`, `Session`, `CacheService`, `PropertiesService`) are available.

## Do NOT

- Treat this tree as the system of record after production cutover
- Port new features here — implement in `src/lib/domain/` instead
- Use `import`/`export` in these files

## Porting workflow

1. Find behaviour in `legacy-gas/WebAppLogic.js`, `LoggerLogic.js`, `index.html`, `Logger.html`, or `Other scripts/`
2. Implement in `src/lib/domain/`
3. Document the mapping in `docs/domain.md` legacy port index
